OL,3,CSafety net to prevent falling debris
OL,4,Cfrom tower block to cost #500,000
OL,6,FSafety netting that will prevent
OL,7,Fdebris from an empty tower block from
OL,8,Ffalling onto the street below will
OL,9,Fcost #500,000, a council has confirmed.
OL,11,FBlackburn and Darwen Council is set to
OL,12,Fcover the 16-storey building, which
OL,13,Fsits on top of the Mall shopping
OL,14,Fcentre in Blackburn's town centre, in
OL,15,Fsafety netting to prevent any debris
OL,16,Ffrom crashing to the ground.
OL,18,FA council report said the building was
OL,19,Fconstructed around 1969 and re-clad in
OL,20,Fthe 1990s, but the tower block has
OL,21,Fremained empty since April 2024.
