OL,6,FSince it was vacated, "routine
OL,7,Finspections and maintenance" have
OL,8,Fidentified "actions to be taken" to
OL,9,Fensure the building remains safe.
OL,11,FExecutive Member for Growth and
OL,12,FDevelopment Labour councillor Quesir
OL,13,FMahmood has asked the council to
OL,14,Fauthorise the spending to make the
OL,15,Fblock and its cladding safe in the
OL,16,Flonger term.
