OL,3,CSafety net to prevent falling debris
OL,4,Cfrom tower block to cost #500,000
OL,6,FMr Mahmood told the council due to the
OL,7,F"age and condition of the external
OL,8,Fcladding system and increasingly
OL,9,Fsevere weather conditions" independent
OL,10,Fassessors "have concluded that the
OL,11,Fentire building should be enveloped as
OL,12,Fsoon as possible".
OL,14,FHe said: "More specifically, the
OL,15,Fsolution identified requires the
OL,16,Finstallation of a full-height debris
OL,17,Fnetting system fixed to the building
OL,18,Fstructure to provide an effective
OL,19,Finterim control measure.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
