OL,4,Cfrom tower block to cost #500,000
OL,6,F"The work - costing up to #500,000 -
OL,7,Fwould "ensure that the building is
OL,8,Fprotected and secure, and the risk
OL,9,Ffrom falling materials is mitigated to
OL,10,Fa minimum."
OL,12,FCouncillor Mustafa Desai, leader of
OL,13,Fthe 4BwD opposition group, said: "I
OL,14,Fsupport the recommendations, but I'm
OL,15,Fconcerned that this building has been
OL,16,Fvacant for several years and presents
OL,17,Fa long-term liability.
OL,19,F"Its future plans are unclear, and
OL,20,Fthis will continue to pose challenges."
